---
// Bento Grid for showcasing features
---

<div class="bento-grid">
  <!-- Large: eBPF Kernel Mode -->
  <div class="bento-item bento-large group">
    <div class="bento-content">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
        <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z" />
        </svg>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[var(--color-cyber)]">Kernel Mode</h3>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-4">XDP programs running at the lowest level. Drop attacks before they touch the network stack.</p>
      <div class="metric-display">
        <span class="metric-value">1%</span>
        <span class="metric-label">CPU Usage</span>
      </div>
      <div class="code-snippet">
        <code class="text-xs font-mono opacity-60">
          // XDP_DROP @ L2<br/>
          return bpf_redirect(ctx, 0);
        </code>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Medium: WASM Hot Reload -->
  <div class="bento-item bento-medium group">
    <div class="bento-content">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
        </svg>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-rust)]">Hot Reload Logic</h3>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-3">Update detection rules without restarting. WASM modules loaded dynamically.</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-mono">
        <span class="text-[var(--color-neon-green)]">‚óè</span>
        <span class="opacity-70">rule_v2.wasm loaded</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Small: Rust Safety -->
  <div class="bento-item bento-small group">
    <div class="bento-content flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center">
      <div class="rust-logo mb-2">ü¶Ä</div>
      <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-[var(--color-rust)]">Memory Safe</h3>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1">Zero-cost abstractions</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Wide: Global Sync -->
  <div class="bento-item bento-wide group">
    <div class="bento-content">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
        </svg>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-cyber)]">CRDT Synchronized State</h3>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Distributed mitigation decisions. Real-time sync via NATS.</p>
      <div class="flex gap-2 mt-3">
        <div class="region-node">üåê US-EAST</div>
        <div class="region-node">üåê EU-WEST</div>
        <div class="region-node">üåê AP-SOUTH</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .bento-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .bento-item {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.9), rgba(5, 5, 5, 0.95));
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .bento-item::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.05), transparent 50%);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .bento-item:hover::before {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .bento-item:hover {
    border-color: rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.5);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .bento-large {
    grid-column: span 2;
    grid-row: span 2;
  }

  .bento-medium {
    grid-column: span 1;
    grid-row: span 2;
  }

  .bento-small {
    grid-column: span 1;
    grid-row: span 1;
  }

  .bento-wide {
    grid-column: span 3;
    grid-row: span 1;
  }

  .bento-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .metric-display {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .metric-value {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    color: var(--color-neon-green);
    text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.5);
  }

  .metric-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .code-snippet {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding: 0.75rem;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--color-cyber);
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
  }

  .rust-logo {
    font-size: 3rem;
    filter: grayscale(100%) brightness(0.8);
    transition: filter 0.3s ease;
  }

  .group:hover .rust-logo {
    filter: grayscale(0%) brightness(1);
  }

  .region-node {
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.3);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    color: var(--color-cyber);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .bento-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .bento-large,
    .bento-medium,
    .bento-small,
    .bento-wide {
      grid-column: span 1;
      grid-row: span 1;
    }
  }
</style>
